                                                       owl:versionIRI <http://ClimOO/climoo/climoo-sdc2/imports/ro-imports#2026-05-29> ;
                                                       rdfs:comment """This file contains ClimOO Ontology imports manually fletched from the Relation Ontology (RO).

Ontology source: https://github.com/oborel/obo-relations/releases/tag/v2025-12-17"""@en ,
                                                                    "We currently imported all object properties we consider useful. We will revise RO imports as needed, possible excluding further object properties not needed for the Purposes of the ClimOO Ontology."@en ;
